---
title: Double Beef Taquitos with Zesty Guacamole
description: Taquitos are a traditional Mexican street food that is typically deep-fried. We’ve baked ours instead, for a healthier twist! They crisp up beautifully in the oven, while the cheesy centre melts to perfection.
